datafield.subfield: Vacunas is a peer-reviewed journal supported by an advisory board of experts in the field of vaccinology. The aim of the journal is to contribute to the dissemination of the scientific advances made in the area of basic and applied research in the field of vaccine-preventable diseases in humans.
